code: import{FETCH_LAKES,CURRENT_LAKE,FAVORITED_LAKE,REMOVE_LAKE}from"./types";export var fetchLakes=function fetchLakes(dispatch){fetch("https://jasonserverhoustonfishing.herokuapp.com/lakes/").then(function(res){return res.json();}).then(function(result){return dispatch({type:FETCH_LAKES,payload:result});});};export var currentLake=function currentLake(dispatch,lake){dispatch({type:CURRENT_LAKE,payload:lake});};export var favoritedLake=function favoritedLake(dispatch,lake){dispatch({type:FAVORITED_LAKE,payload:lake});};export var removeLake=function removeLake(dispatch,lake){dispatch({type:REMOVE_LAKE,payload:lake});};
